nl_querry: What is the amount of the funds that the Vice President received? 'Vice President' is a position of Student Club; funds received refers to amount.
llm_querry: SELECT SUM(T1.amount) FROM income AS T1 JOIN member AS T2 ON T1.link_to_member = T2.member_id WHERE T2.position = 'Vice President'
gold_querry: SELECT T2.amount FROM member AS T1 INNER JOIN income AS T2 ON T1.member_id = T2.link_to_member WHERE T1.position = 'Vice President'
